title: Health Worker
description: A person working in the field of health care. This may be used to represent a doctor, nurse, or pharmacist.
apple_vendor_description: The health worker emoji on Apple devices presents a compassionate figure, often depicted with a stethoscope around their neck and wearing a uniform that suggests care and professionalism. Apple's signature glossy 3D shading gives this emoji a lifelike texture, with smooth gradients and realistic lighting that convey trust and dedication. This symbol is frequently used to express gratitude for medical professionals, acknowledge healthcare efforts, or represent the medical field in conversations on Apple devices.
